[div class=p 
	"In 
	[em 
		"Kanshakudama-nage Kantarou no Toukaidou Gojuusan-tsugi
	]em
	" (かんしゃく玉投げカン太郎の東海道五十三次), you play a fireworks-maker traveling the 
	[a href=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tōkaidō_%28road%29 rel=noopener external nofollow 
		"Tōkaidō road
	]a
	". The game actually bears quite a resemblance to the actual geography of the Tōkaidō road; famous landmarks, rivers, and flora types are reproduced as well as they can be given the limitations of the Famicom.
	$LF
]div
